        "service_label_ankara-web-tasarim": "Freelance Web Design",
        "service_title_ankara-web-tasarim": "Ankara Web Design Services",
        "service_desc_ankara-web-tasarim": "Designing high-performance, SEO-focused, and modern websites for premium brands, industrial firms, and high-end businesses in Ankara.",
        "service_sec1_title_ankara-web-tasarim": "Tailored Premium Web Design",
        "service_sec1_body_ankara-web-tasarim": "\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed\">Having a digital presence is no longer just a necessity; it is your brand's most powerful showcase. In my Ankara web design services, I step away from template designs to deliver custom solutions where every pixel is tailored to your brand's vision. Built with Vanilla JS and modern CSS, these websites are entirely free from the performance issues and security vulnerabilities of ready-made systems like WordPress.</p>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed\">Translating your physical prestige into the digital world begins with representing your corporate identity correctly. By using premium typography like Playfair Display, minimalist layouts, and fluid micro-animations, I turn the user journey into a delightful experience. My designs are not just visually stunning; they are fully aligned with Google's search algorithms.</p>\n",
        "service_sec2_title_ankara-web-tasarim": "SEO-Ready Infrastructure & Core Web Vitals",
        "service_sec2_body_ankara-web-tasarim": "\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed\">Google directly measures your website's speed and technical health to determine rankings. I place metrics known as Core Web Vitals—LCP (Largest Contentful Paint), FID (First Input Delay), and CLS (Cumulative Layout Shift)—at the center of my development workflow. Bulky websites that take seconds to load cause you to lose potential customers.</p>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed\">By keeping page load speeds under 1 second, I actively boost your conversion rates. I develop fast, secure, and Google-compliant websites for corporate firms in Ankara's leading business hubs (Ostim, Ivedik, Çankaya, Bilkent) to help them compete globally. Technical SEO is built directly into the foundation.</p>\n",
        "service_sec3_title_ankara-web-tasarim": "Conversion & Growth Oriented UI/UX",
        "service_sec3_body_ankara-web-tasarim": "\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed\">A beautiful and fast website is only successful when it converts visitors into clients or business partners. In my freelance web design services, I craft clear Call-to-Action pathways that make user actions (submitting a form, calling, or emailing) effortless.</p>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed\">With fully responsive layouts, users get a flawless experience across all viewports—from desktop screens to tablets and mobile phones. Elevate your corporate credibility and sales with a modern UI design that powers your growth strategy.</p>\n",
        "service_sidebar_ankara-web-tasarim": "\n            <li>✓ Custom UI Design</li>\n            <li>✓ Clean Vanilla JS Code</li>\n            <li>✓ SEO-Ready Infrastructure</li>\n            <li>✓ Core Web Vitals Performance</li>\n            <li>✓ Mobile-First Responsiveness</li>\n            <li>✓ SSL Security & Form Integration</li>\n        ",
        "service_cta_ankara-web-tasarim": "Get a Quote",
        "service_side_title_ankara-web-tasarim": "Service Summary",
        "faq_q_hukuk-burosu-web-tasarimi_0": "How is a legal website made compliant with TBB rules?",
        "faq_a_hukuk-burosu-web-tasarimi_0": "The website avoids advertising, commercial slogans, and claims of superiority. It focuses purely on providing corporate information and sharing legal articles.",
        "faq_q_hukuk-burosu-web-tasarimi_1": "Can we update the articles on the website ourselves?",
        "faq_a_hukuk-burosu-web-tasarimi_1": "Yes, I integrate an easy-to-use content management system (CMS) where lawyers or office staff can easily publish articles and news updates.",
        "service_label_hukuk-burosu-web-tasarimi": "For Law Firms",
        "service_title_hukuk-burosu-web-tasarimi": "Law Firm & Lawyer Web Design",
        "service_desc_hukuk-burosu-web-tasarimi": "Designing prestigious, corporate, and respected legal websites fully compliant with the Turkish Bar Association (TBB) regulations.",
        "service_sec1_title_hukuk-burosu-web-tasarimi": "Fully Compliant with TBB Regulations",
        "service_sec1_body_hukuk-burosu-web-tasarimi": "\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed\">Having a digital presence is of great importance for lawyers and law firms. However, the most critical element in designing legal websites is full compliance with the Turkish Bar Association (TBB) Advertising Prohibition Regulation. In my designs, I offer a corporate prestige that inspires trust while strictly adhering to ethical rules and legal limits.</p>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed\">I build a clean interface architecture that is informative, carries no advertising or unfair competition elements, and projects a transparent and respected stance in full compliance with TBB legislation. I reflect the prestige of your law firm with dignified color palettes and corporate typography.</p>\n",
        "service_sec2_title_hukuk-burosu-web-tasarimi": "Client Communication & Article Publishing",
        "service_sec2_body_hukuk-burosu-web-tasarimi": "\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed\">One of the most important digital assets for law firms is the ability to share articles and legal analyses in their fields of expertise. Thanks to the article publishing infrastructure I integrate, you can easily share legal updates and rank high on search engines with your expertise.</p>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed\">Encrypted forms that allow clients to contact you under strict confidentiality, physical address details, Google Maps integration, and office hours are positioned in full compliance with legal guidelines.</p>\n",
        "service_sec3_title_hukuk-burosu-web-tasarimi": "Prestige & Corporate Credibility",
        "service_sec3_body_hukuk-burosu-web-tasarimi": "\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed\">There is no room for visual clutter or exaggerated animations on legal websites. I achieve a noble harmony using classic serif fonts like Playfair Display, corporate navy blues, charcoal, and warm gold accents. The feelings inspired when a client visits your site will be trust, dignity, and professionalism.</p>\n<p class=\"mb-6 leading-relaxed\">With ultra-fast loading times and seamless mobile experiences, I ensure that clients with urgent legal needs can easily reach your site at any moment.</p>\n",
